      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0586P0-03313'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0586P0_19980225_GCR_50' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 82 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0586P0-03314'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0586P0_19980225_GCR_51' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Falconer of Thoroton</span> moved Amendment No. 83:
        <q>Page 16, line 43, after ("principle") insert ("(except to the extent to which it requires compliance with the conditions in Schedules 2 and 3)").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0586P0-03315'>
