        Clause 38 [<span class="italic">Enforcement notices</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0586P0-03489'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0586P0_19980225_GCR_226' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Viscount Astor</span> moved Amendment No. 120A:
        <q>Page 21, line 20, at end insert ("or, in Scotland, personal injury").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0586P0-03490'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0586P0_19980225_GCR_227' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
