        Clause 43 [<span class="italic">Determination by Commissioner as to the special purposes</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0586P0-03533'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0586P0_19980225_GCR_270' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
